WEBVTT

02:08.590 --> 02:09.850
Tai Xuan Acupuncture?

02:09.910 --> 02:11.710
It really is the Tai Xuan Acupuncture.

02:11.710 --> 02:14.080
I saw it recorded
in an ancient medical text.

02:14.080 --> 02:15.630
I thought it had been lost long ago.

02:15.630 --> 02:18.280
Never did I imagine it would
still be preserved among the people.

02:18.280 --> 02:19.680
After a lifetime devoted to medicine,

02:19.680 --> 02:21.960
to behold
the Tai Xuan Acupuncture once more—

02:21.960 --> 02:23.710
I would die with no regrets.

03:06.800 --> 03:08.520
I see.

03:09.520 --> 03:10.520
The Tai Xuan Acupuncture

03:10.520 --> 03:11.590
is really amazing.

03:12.680 --> 03:13.630
Physician Chen.

03:13.630 --> 03:14.680
To be honest,

03:15.030 --> 03:17.800
what I used just now was indeed
the Tai Xuan Acupuncture.

03:17.800 --> 03:19.310
Regrettably, my skills are limited—

03:19.310 --> 03:21.040
I have only learned its basics.

03:21.190 --> 03:23.079
Whether General Xiao
will survive the night unharmed

03:23.079 --> 03:24.520
remains to be seen.

03:24.520 --> 03:26.280
Physician Han, you are too modest.

03:26.280 --> 03:27.240
Physician Chen.

03:27.400 --> 03:29.520
The root of this illness is poison,

03:29.520 --> 03:30.910
and it's not contagious.

03:30.910 --> 03:33.079
We were helpless
because our treatment methods

03:33.079 --> 03:35.010
had been misguided from the start.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.360
Look.

03:36.680 --> 03:38.680
The blood has congealed into powder.

03:38.680 --> 03:39.310
Far from smelling foul,

03:39.310 --> 03:41.170
it carries an unusual fragrance.

03:42.680 --> 03:43.400
Right.

03:44.280 --> 03:45.240
You mean that

03:45.240 --> 03:46.360
General Xiao took the medicine

03:46.360 --> 03:47.710
as a way of fighting poison with poison,

03:47.710 --> 03:48.910
but the toxin
remained trapped in his body.

03:48.910 --> 03:50.910
Only with the aid of acupuncture
can the poison be expelled.

03:50.910 --> 03:52.520
This use of acupuncture
to expel the toxin

03:52.520 --> 03:54.380
was merely a fortunate accident.

03:55.079 --> 03:57.680
Today, I have truly witnessed
something extraordinary.

03:57.680 --> 03:58.520
Physician Han.

03:58.520 --> 04:00.310
You are a talent of your generation,

04:00.310 --> 04:01.970
worthy of the highest praise.

04:02.080 --> 04:03.680
You flatter me, Physician Chen.

04:03.680 --> 04:05.630
Now that the medicine
has proven successful,

04:05.630 --> 04:07.870
I must hurry to
prepare it for the villagers

04:07.870 --> 04:09.630
and let everyone know the good news.

04:09.630 --> 04:10.840
As for General Xiao,

04:10.840 --> 04:13.430
please stay here
for another night, Physician Chen.

04:13.430 --> 04:14.240
Okay.

04:14.680 --> 04:15.840
You brought General Xiao

04:15.840 --> 04:17.630
back from the verge of death.

04:17.720 --> 04:19.040
I'm confident

04:19.040 --> 04:20.480
I can ensure his safety.

04:20.680 --> 04:21.410
In that case,

04:21.680 --> 04:22.390
thank you.

04:40.680 --> 04:41.480
General Xiao.

04:41.680 --> 04:42.600
You're awake.

04:43.430 --> 04:44.510
Looks like

04:44.510 --> 04:46.240
death didn't take me this time.

04:46.480 --> 04:47.270
It was Physician Han

04:47.270 --> 04:49.000
who brought you back.

04:51.120 --> 04:51.950
Where is Yunling?

04:51.950 --> 04:53.240
Where is she?

04:53.310 --> 04:54.110
General Xiao.

04:54.310 --> 04:56.680
Risking your own life to test the medicine
was a righteous act.

04:56.680 --> 04:58.270
Physician Han spent the whole night
preparing the remedy

04:58.270 --> 04:59.510
for the patients—

04:59.510 --> 05:00.480
she probably

05:00.680 --> 05:01.800
hasn't rested yet.

05:02.120 --> 05:03.050
I'll go find her.

05:09.240 --> 05:12.480
When will they come out?

05:13.310 --> 05:15.190
Why aren't they out yet?

05:16.600 --> 05:19.310
They're out. They're out.

05:24.000 --> 05:25.800
They're out.

05:57.800 --> 05:59.190
My fellow villagers.

05:59.480 --> 06:00.480
Everyone.

06:01.070 --> 06:02.040
We should all

06:02.040 --> 06:04.840
be grateful
to Physician Han for saving our lives.

06:05.430 --> 06:07.720
Thank you for saving our lives.

06:08.190 --> 06:10.310
Thank you for saving our lives.

06:10.310 --> 06:11.120
Everyone,

06:11.360 --> 06:12.800
you can go home.

06:13.430 --> 06:17.240
Let's go home.

06:17.920 --> 06:18.750
Physician Han.

06:18.750 --> 06:19.950
We're going home too.

06:20.000 --> 06:20.560
Okay.

06:20.920 --> 06:21.780
Physician Han.

06:21.870 --> 06:23.040
Now that the patients have recovered,

06:23.040 --> 06:24.630
we shall return to the capital.

06:24.630 --> 06:25.270
Farewell.

06:51.270 --> 06:52.400
You've worked hard.

06:55.390 --> 06:56.720
It's all over now.

07:09.510 --> 07:11.680
If you had listened to me

07:11.870 --> 07:14.240
and eliminated
the infected villagers then and there,

07:14.240 --> 07:16.800
none of this would have happened.

07:16.800 --> 07:17.600
Lord Li.

07:18.480 --> 07:20.340
You don't agree with that, do you?

07:20.600 --> 07:21.920
Your Majesty.

07:22.160 --> 07:24.920
I think Lord Zhang is right.

07:25.270 --> 07:26.720
After all, the plague

07:26.720 --> 07:29.000
that struck
the people of Jinglan years ago

07:29.000 --> 07:32.070
is still vivid in my mind.

07:32.070 --> 07:33.270
It was

07:33.270 --> 07:34.390
a terrible sight.

07:34.390 --> 07:37.270
Even now, the thought of it
fills me with fear.

07:37.390 --> 07:38.390
Your Majesty.

07:39.240 --> 07:42.190
I think what Lord Li said makes sense.

07:42.190 --> 07:44.510
Your Majesty, though you are merciful,

07:44.600 --> 07:47.000
in matters of such great importance,

07:47.000 --> 07:49.480
there must be no room for error.

07:49.870 --> 07:50.830
Otherwise,

07:50.920 --> 07:52.360
your wise rule

07:52.360 --> 07:54.390
and the entire land of Jinglan

07:54.720 --> 07:57.240
will be brought to ruin.

07:57.240 --> 07:57.830
Right.

07:57.830 --> 07:58.720
Your Majesty.

07:59.870 --> 08:00.600
Lord Fei.

08:01.270 --> 08:02.270
What do you think?

08:03.600 --> 08:04.600
I think

08:05.480 --> 08:07.190
both lords have a point.

08:08.120 --> 08:09.600
But I still hold that

08:10.190 --> 08:11.600
as our ancestors taught us,

08:11.600 --> 08:14.200
among all under Heaven,
the people come first.

08:14.510 --> 08:16.630
Though Huangpi Village
is but a small place,

08:16.630 --> 08:18.390
the villagers remain His Majesty's people.

08:18.390 --> 08:20.270
Even in the time of the late Emperor,

08:20.270 --> 08:22.040
when the plague was at its worst,

08:22.040 --> 08:23.160
we never

08:23.160 --> 08:25.120
give up any citizen.

08:25.870 --> 08:27.120
Well said.

08:28.040 --> 08:29.270
I am a wise ruler.

08:30.390 --> 08:32.480
As long as it is not the very last resort,

08:32.480 --> 08:35.270
I won't give up on anyone in Jinglan.

08:35.510 --> 08:37.630
There's news from Xiao Chi.

08:37.909 --> 08:38.960
Now,

08:38.960 --> 08:40.870
Huangpi Village is under control.

08:40.870 --> 08:41.720
Lord Fei.

08:42.030 --> 08:44.750
Do not lie before His Majesty,

08:45.240 --> 08:46.080
or you will

08:46.270 --> 08:48.510
be punished for deceiving the Emperor.

08:48.670 --> 08:49.360
Lord Zhang.

08:49.840 --> 08:51.360
If I have spoken falsely,

08:51.360 --> 08:52.820
I will accept punishment.

08:55.480 --> 08:56.440
Your Majesty,

08:56.440 --> 08:57.510
a report from the front—

08:57.510 --> 08:59.030
Huangpi Village has been
freed of the plague,

08:59.030 --> 09:00.560
and all villagers are safe.

09:01.870 --> 09:02.670
Good.

09:03.270 --> 09:04.960
Heaven has indeed blessed Jinglan.

09:04.960 --> 09:06.000
Xiao Chi

09:06.320 --> 09:07.720
is worthy of great merit.

09:08.440 --> 09:09.040
Fei Zheng.

09:09.120 --> 09:09.910
Yes, Your Majesty.

09:09.910 --> 09:11.240
Go to Huangpi Village

09:11.630 --> 09:13.560
and bring General Xiao back for me.

09:13.630 --> 09:15.510
I'll personally reward him.

09:16.480 --> 09:17.000
Yes.

09:17.390 --> 09:18.190
Your Majesty.

09:18.480 --> 09:19.600
Lord Zhang.

09:19.840 --> 09:20.670
Yes.

09:20.960 --> 09:22.360
Please go there

09:22.360 --> 09:24.080
and escort

09:24.510 --> 09:25.630
General Xiao back

09:26.150 --> 09:27.600
for me.

09:30.000 --> 09:30.750
Yes.

09:31.150 --> 09:32.320
Your Majesty.

09:35.200 --> 09:37.720
Come on. Pour the wine.

09:37.720 --> 09:38.510
Fill it up.

09:38.630 --> 09:40.270
Fill it up.

09:40.320 --> 09:41.120
Here you go.

09:41.120 --> 09:41.960
Physician Han.

09:41.960 --> 09:42.760
General Xiao.

09:43.510 --> 09:44.870
Without your help,

09:45.030 --> 09:46.270
Huangpi Village would never

09:46.270 --> 09:48.630
have overcome the Death Plague.

09:48.870 --> 09:50.440
On behalf of the villagers,

09:50.440 --> 09:51.600
I thank you both.

09:52.270 --> 09:54.240
Please accept this bow.

09:55.720 --> 09:58.270
Please accept our bow of gratitude.

10:03.870 --> 10:05.200
Please get up.

10:05.480 --> 10:06.510
Get up.

10:08.030 --> 10:10.000
It's my duty.

10:10.080 --> 10:10.840
This is the result

10:10.840 --> 10:12.270
of everyone's effort.

10:12.480 --> 10:14.120
Chief, there is no need for such courtesy.

10:14.120 --> 10:15.030
Please get up.

10:15.720 --> 10:16.720
Please get up.

10:16.840 --> 10:17.720
Get up.

10:20.390 --> 10:21.240
Everyone,

10:21.870 --> 10:23.270
let's toast General Xiao

10:23.270 --> 10:24.720
and Physician Han.

10:24.720 --> 10:26.480
To General Xiao.

10:26.480 --> 10:28.200
To Physician Han.

10:47.030 --> 10:47.840
Xiao Chi.

10:50.120 --> 10:52.180
I will definitely cure your illness.

11:01.240 --> 11:03.370
It's alright even if it can't be cured.

11:04.270 --> 11:06.510
Don't you want to live well?

11:10.200 --> 11:11.080
I do.

11:13.080 --> 11:13.910
Of course I do.

11:14.840 --> 11:15.720
But I'm afraid

11:15.910 --> 11:18.640
in the end, it will all be
nothing but an illusion.

11:20.720 --> 11:23.000
We have to look at the bright side.

11:24.510 --> 11:26.240
Though this illusion is unreal,

11:26.240 --> 11:28.170
it once illuminated the darkness.

11:29.600 --> 11:31.120
Just like life itself—

11:31.120 --> 11:32.480
though filled with hardships,

11:32.480 --> 11:34.120
there is always a ray of light

11:34.270 --> 11:35.400
that shines upon us.

11:37.840 --> 11:38.630
Yes.

11:39.670 --> 11:40.840
In every heart,

11:41.960 --> 11:44.120
there is a warm light of its own.

11:55.240 --> 11:56.550
General, Physician Han.

11:56.550 --> 11:57.270
Zheng.

11:59.600 --> 12:01.460
You two seem to be in good spirits.

12:01.510 --> 12:03.240
However, even the best of moods

12:03.320 --> 12:05.580
cannot allow you to stay here any longer.

12:05.600 --> 12:06.630
Chu has ordered me

12:06.630 --> 12:07.890
to bring you both back.

12:08.120 --> 12:09.000
We can talk

12:09.200 --> 12:10.860
once we return to the capital.

12:11.510 --> 12:12.320
Okay.

12:20.390 --> 12:21.320
Your Highness.

12:21.670 --> 12:24.200
His Majesty went to
the Xiao Residence again.

12:27.720 --> 12:29.840
I would like to see

12:30.910 --> 12:32.710
the one he is so concerned about.

12:38.790 --> 12:40.120
That hairpin is pretty.

12:40.240 --> 12:40.910
Jin Xi.

12:40.910 --> 12:42.200
It suits you well.

12:46.670 --> 12:48.240
As your female official,

12:48.510 --> 12:51.080
I am not allowed
to wear any extra accessories.

12:51.080 --> 12:53.080
I don't even mind, so why should you?

12:53.240 --> 12:54.910
Jin Xi, get me an eyebrow brush.

12:54.910 --> 12:55.480
Okay.

12:56.120 --> 12:58.320
The Eldest Princess has arrived!

13:02.910 --> 13:04.240
Who are you?

13:04.240 --> 13:06.390
The Eldest Princess of
Jinglan has arrived.

13:06.390 --> 13:08.600
Have your princess kneel to pay respects.

13:08.600 --> 13:09.930
Liu Chu's elder sister?

13:16.240 --> 13:17.440
You may leave now.

13:18.270 --> 13:20.720
I want to talk to the Princess of Changmo.

13:35.240 --> 13:36.000
Look at you.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.080
Get up.

13:39.440 --> 13:41.000
We'll be a family soon.

13:41.000 --> 13:43.130
There's no need for such formalities.

13:43.240 --> 13:44.510
You are

13:44.790 --> 13:45.720
so beautiful.

13:46.670 --> 13:49.130
Princess of Changmo,
you truly are a beauty.

13:49.840 --> 13:51.080
Thank you, Your Highness.

13:51.080 --> 13:52.360
You can call me Wanyu.

13:53.440 --> 13:54.000
Okay.

13:54.480 --> 13:55.240
Wanyu.

13:58.120 --> 13:59.960
What brings you here today?

14:00.510 --> 14:02.080
Liu Chu didn't send me.

14:02.270 --> 14:03.910
I came on my own to see you.

14:04.630 --> 14:06.600
Is Liu Chu busy?

14:08.480 --> 14:09.480
I mean,

14:09.750 --> 14:11.750
I've been in the capital for so long,

14:11.790 --> 14:13.440
and he has never summoned me.

14:13.790 --> 14:14.960
I don't even know

14:14.960 --> 14:16.910
when the marriage ceremony will be held.

14:16.910 --> 14:19.910
You haven't seen him
since you arrived in the capital?

14:23.910 --> 14:24.750
He has

14:24.840 --> 14:26.390
long been busy with court affairs.

14:26.390 --> 14:28.320
Even I find it difficult to see him.

14:28.910 --> 14:29.960
But I believe

14:30.360 --> 14:32.440
he won't keep you here for too long.

14:33.790 --> 14:34.600
That's good.

14:35.720 --> 14:37.520
Liu Chu has always called me Xie.

14:37.870 --> 14:40.870
Although the marriage ceremony
hasn't been held yet,

14:41.270 --> 14:42.600
I like you.

14:42.910 --> 14:44.270
You can also call me Xie.

14:45.790 --> 14:46.550
Xie.

14:52.080 --> 14:52.750
Xie.

14:53.000 --> 14:55.600
Is Liu Chu as good-looking as you?

14:57.240 --> 14:58.240
We are born

14:58.240 --> 14:59.630
of the same mother.

15:00.320 --> 15:01.790
Not only do we look alike,

15:02.240 --> 15:04.000
even our personalities

15:04.360 --> 15:05.510
are the same.

15:06.910 --> 15:07.720
That's good.

15:08.080 --> 15:10.940
I was worried Liu Chu
might be a very serious person.

15:11.600 --> 15:12.390
Xie.

15:12.720 --> 15:14.360
What does Liu Chu like?

15:15.200 --> 15:16.200
He...

15:18.390 --> 15:20.080
He will like you very much.

15:29.840 --> 15:31.640
What do you think of the capital?

15:31.720 --> 15:32.790
The city walls

15:32.790 --> 15:34.200
are tall and imposing,

15:34.480 --> 15:35.940
the streets are bustling,

15:37.240 --> 15:39.040
and there is plenty of good food.

15:40.030 --> 15:40.910
What else?

15:41.870 --> 15:44.120
I haven't been to other places yet.

15:44.720 --> 15:45.870
When you enter the palace,

15:45.870 --> 15:47.600
I'll take you around properly.

15:48.200 --> 15:49.080
Thank you, Xie.

15:50.270 --> 15:50.960
Xie.

15:51.390 --> 15:52.120
What else

15:52.120 --> 15:53.720
does he like to do?

15:54.720 --> 15:55.910
What does he like to do?

15:55.910 --> 15:56.440
Yeah.

15:58.120 --> 15:59.840
He likes me to clean his ears for him.

15:59.840 --> 16:00.770
Does this count?

16:00.910 --> 16:02.510
You know how to do ear cleaning?

16:02.510 --> 16:03.000
Yes.

16:03.440 --> 16:04.360
Xie.

16:04.360 --> 16:06.030
Could you teach me sometime?

16:06.030 --> 16:07.000
Of course.

16:07.630 --> 16:08.630
But

16:08.630 --> 16:11.030
you have to wait
until you enter the palace.

16:11.390 --> 16:12.870
Thank you, Xie.

16:14.390 --> 16:16.600
When the marriage alliance
was first proposed,

16:16.600 --> 16:18.530
all the officials were against it.

16:19.150 --> 16:20.440
Only I supported it.

16:21.000 --> 16:22.240
Now it seems

16:22.720 --> 16:24.080
it was the right choice.

16:29.080 --> 16:30.240
This hairpin

16:30.320 --> 16:32.440
was left to me by my late mother.

16:33.360 --> 16:34.620
I want to give it to you.

16:35.360 --> 16:36.200
Xie.

16:36.200 --> 16:37.750
It's such a precious gift.

16:37.750 --> 16:39.840
This is my love for you and Liu Chu.

16:40.150 --> 16:41.390
You can't refuse it.

16:44.550 --> 16:45.550
Thank you, Xie.

16:48.670 --> 16:49.790
Liu Chu and I

16:50.030 --> 16:51.440
will be happy.

17:02.600 --> 17:03.240
My Lord.

17:12.069 --> 17:13.310
This tea doesn't seem

17:14.480 --> 17:16.480
as fragrant as usual today.

17:18.160 --> 17:20.000
It was made just the way

17:20.000 --> 17:21.349
you always prefer.

17:24.000 --> 17:24.550
My Lord.

17:25.069 --> 17:26.200
Black moves first, white follows—

17:26.200 --> 17:27.960
you've turned the tables.

17:30.720 --> 17:31.960
There is no right or wrong,

17:31.960 --> 17:33.720
no winning or losing.

17:34.240 --> 17:35.110
Take it.

17:36.590 --> 17:38.960
It's just a game of chess.

17:39.680 --> 17:40.240
My Lord.

17:41.240 --> 17:43.370
I didn't expect Xiao Chi and the others

17:43.440 --> 17:45.700
to survive resolve the plague this time.

17:46.200 --> 17:47.550
Fate is decided

17:47.550 --> 17:48.640
by heaven.

17:49.680 --> 17:51.240
Those meant to live die,

17:51.830 --> 17:53.760
and those who should die are alive.

17:54.240 --> 17:55.500
You're right, My Lord.

17:56.110 --> 17:57.590
So,

17:57.590 --> 17:59.450
what happened in Huangpi Village

17:59.590 --> 18:00.830
is just over?

18:04.240 --> 18:06.400
Do you really believe

18:06.790 --> 18:08.520
they can cure all the patients?

18:08.640 --> 18:10.030
Who knows?

18:10.350 --> 18:11.240
Besides,

18:11.240 --> 18:12.350
even if they can be cured,

18:12.350 --> 18:13.960
who can guarantee

18:14.400 --> 18:16.310
it won't break out again?

18:18.240 --> 18:19.680
You mean...

18:21.350 --> 18:22.070
My Lord.

18:22.400 --> 18:23.830
You are the Grand Secretary now.

18:23.830 --> 18:24.880
In some matters,

18:24.880 --> 18:26.010
we cannot hesitate.

18:26.830 --> 18:28.590
We can't allow even the slightest chance

18:28.590 --> 18:32.160
of this plague returning.

18:36.350 --> 18:39.000
No wonder
you've been with me for so many years.

18:40.200 --> 18:41.240
That's exactly

18:41.510 --> 18:43.200
what I was thinking.

18:45.720 --> 18:47.720
The tragedy of eight years ago

18:48.200 --> 18:50.590
is chilling to think about.

18:51.200 --> 18:52.960
Send someone to deal with it—

18:54.160 --> 18:55.110
swiftly,

18:55.590 --> 18:57.110
and without causing any pain.

18:57.110 --> 18:57.790
Yes.

18:58.830 --> 18:59.720
Then...

19:00.160 --> 19:02.090
what about Xiao Chi and the others?

19:02.200 --> 19:05.510
It won't be that easy for him

19:06.270 --> 19:07.830
to report to His Majesty.

19:07.830 --> 19:08.590
Don't worry.

19:09.350 --> 19:10.790
I know what to do.

19:19.310 --> 19:20.960
Only now does this tea

19:21.440 --> 19:23.350
begin to have any fragrance.

19:31.400 --> 19:32.400
Please enjoy.

19:32.550 --> 19:33.720
I'll go take a look around.

19:33.720 --> 19:33.960
Here.

19:33.960 --> 19:34.560
Thank you.

19:36.830 --> 19:37.790
What do you think, Zheng?

19:37.790 --> 19:39.990
Isn't Jinglan's scenery magnificent?

19:40.590 --> 19:43.160
The beauty of the land
is truly awe-inspiring.

19:43.160 --> 19:44.510
May the realm be at peace

19:44.920 --> 19:46.580
and the land remain unharmed.

19:48.000 --> 19:50.030
Changmo also has many beautiful sights.

19:50.030 --> 19:52.440
Every land has its own beauty—

19:53.550 --> 19:55.510
it is only war and prejudice

19:56.000 --> 19:57.440
that blind people to it.

19:58.270 --> 19:59.440
Physician Han,

19:59.440 --> 20:01.030
that was very profound.

20:03.030 --> 20:03.830
I believe that

20:04.110 --> 20:05.000
in Changmo,

20:05.270 --> 20:07.000
there are also people of simple hearts,

20:07.000 --> 20:08.590
longing for peace and stability

20:08.590 --> 20:09.750
just as we are.

20:12.550 --> 20:14.750
May the world be at peace,

20:14.750 --> 20:16.280
and may there be no more war.

20:16.480 --> 20:17.080
Well said.

20:17.550 --> 20:19.070
To a world without war—

20:19.070 --> 20:19.530
cheers.

20:21.750 --> 20:22.720
Then...

20:23.000 --> 20:24.440
to a world without war—

20:24.680 --> 20:25.350
cheers.

20:27.070 --> 20:28.530
You'd better not drink it.

20:35.440 --> 20:37.350
You have all had a hard journey.

20:37.550 --> 20:40.200
But after spending so long
in Huangpi Village,

20:40.200 --> 20:40.880
there may

20:41.030 --> 20:43.590
still be toxins left in your bodies.

20:43.960 --> 20:45.680
If those were brought back to the capital,

20:45.680 --> 20:47.680
the consequences would be serious.

20:48.240 --> 20:49.030
Lord Zhang.

20:49.400 --> 20:52.000
Everyone in Huangpi Village
has already been cured,

20:52.000 --> 20:54.000
and there has been no relapse for so long.

20:54.000 --> 20:56.160
On what grounds do you claim
there are still toxins left?

20:56.160 --> 20:57.000
Lord Zhang.

20:57.310 --> 20:58.830
His Majesty said he would

20:58.830 --> 21:01.030
personally reward General Xiao.

21:01.440 --> 21:02.920
This can't be delayed.

21:03.070 --> 21:04.160
Lord Fei.

21:04.790 --> 21:05.920
I am only thinking

21:05.920 --> 21:08.350
of the safety
of the people in the capital.

21:08.750 --> 21:10.400
Now everyone in the capital

21:10.400 --> 21:12.640
already knows that
General Xiao has earned merit,

21:12.640 --> 21:13.720
so there is no need

21:13.880 --> 21:15.550
to rush the reward.

21:15.720 --> 21:16.510
I think

21:16.510 --> 21:18.680
it would be better for you

21:19.240 --> 21:21.350
to wait a few more days

21:21.550 --> 21:23.160
and enter the palace

21:23.350 --> 21:24.920
once you're cleared.

21:26.030 --> 21:27.630
I am doing this for the safety

21:27.640 --> 21:31.070
of His Majesty
and the people in the capital.

21:31.880 --> 21:32.920
I advise that

21:33.240 --> 21:34.680
you return to the residence

21:34.680 --> 21:37.340
and remain under observation
for several days.

21:41.550 --> 21:42.590
In that case,

21:42.750 --> 21:44.310
we will return to our residence and wait.

21:44.310 --> 21:46.400
Lord Zhang, please inform His Majesty

21:46.400 --> 21:49.060
that we are ready
to enter the palace at any time.

21:50.110 --> 21:51.310
Don't worry.

21:51.550 --> 21:53.510
I will pass it on.

21:54.920 --> 21:56.160
Open the city gate.

21:57.160 --> 22:00.880
Escort General Xiao and Physician Han
back to the residence.

22:02.720 --> 22:04.110
General Xiao.

22:04.550 --> 22:05.920
Please.

22:25.000 --> 22:26.200
What does this mean?

22:26.480 --> 22:28.680
Are they putting us under house arrest?

22:30.440 --> 22:31.900
Even if it is house arrest,

22:32.110 --> 22:33.840
why keep the two of us
together?

22:37.160 --> 22:38.680
We should take things as they come.

22:38.680 --> 22:40.410
It's better than going to jail.

22:40.590 --> 22:42.000
Why should we be imprisoned?

22:42.000 --> 22:43.110
We're there to save people,

22:43.110 --> 22:44.310
not to kill anyone.

22:45.830 --> 22:46.960
I don't understand.

22:47.030 --> 22:48.510
He was the one who sent us there,

22:48.510 --> 22:50.510
and also the one
who sent people to bring us back.

22:50.510 --> 22:52.110
Now that we're back,

22:52.240 --> 22:54.550
he still wants to detain us
under house arrest?

22:54.550 --> 22:56.750
How many Emperors are there in Jinglan?

22:57.830 --> 22:58.690
Physician Han.

22:58.920 --> 22:59.920
Watch your mouth.

23:12.680 --> 23:15.590
How long will Xiao Chi and the others
be under house arrest?

23:15.590 --> 23:16.440
A month.

23:17.880 --> 23:18.790
Was the outbreak in Huangpi Village

23:18.790 --> 23:20.160
really cured by them?

23:20.590 --> 23:21.550
Of course.

23:24.720 --> 23:26.110
Do you know something?

23:26.830 --> 23:27.880
How is that possible?

23:27.880 --> 23:29.200
I serve the princess in the residence

23:29.200 --> 23:30.070
every day.

23:30.070 --> 23:31.530
How would I know anything?

23:33.270 --> 23:34.880
The plague in Huangpi Village

23:34.880 --> 23:36.160
came unexpectedly,

23:36.400 --> 23:38.400
but fortunately it was
brought under control in time.

23:38.400 --> 23:39.590
The Imperial Medical Academy

23:39.590 --> 23:41.590
is now investigating its source.

23:42.480 --> 23:44.010
Investigating its source?

23:45.440 --> 23:47.700
Are you truly uninvolved in this matter?

23:48.200 --> 23:49.400
I know nothing.

23:50.440 --> 23:51.680
Before you came here,

23:51.880 --> 23:53.000
you told me

23:53.070 --> 23:55.350
your only duty was to protect the princess

23:55.350 --> 23:57.200
and ensure the marriage alliance.

23:57.200 --> 23:58.800
If you have any other orders,

23:58.830 --> 24:00.090
you should tell me now.

24:00.510 --> 24:02.000
If anything goes wrong,

24:02.350 --> 24:04.010
I won't be able to protect you.

24:04.200 --> 24:05.550
I know what to do.

24:07.350 --> 24:07.950
By the way,

24:08.310 --> 24:09.960
what kind of person is Liu Xie?

24:09.960 --> 24:12.090
Why are you suddenly asking about her?

24:12.550 --> 24:14.750
She came to see the princess a while ago.

24:16.720 --> 24:17.550
She

24:18.350 --> 24:19.680
controls the treasury,

24:19.790 --> 24:21.190
excels in state affairs,

24:21.400 --> 24:22.830
understands people well,

24:22.830 --> 24:24.490
and sees through everything.

24:24.510 --> 24:25.400
What about

24:25.550 --> 24:26.680
her relationship with Liu Chu?

24:26.680 --> 24:27.830
They are siblings,

24:27.830 --> 24:29.490
and they are extremely close.

24:29.640 --> 24:31.750
Will she interfere with the marriage...

24:31.750 --> 24:32.590
No.

24:33.960 --> 24:34.720
The alliance

24:35.000 --> 24:36.330
concerns both nations.

24:36.350 --> 24:38.310
It is not for her to decide.

24:38.830 --> 24:39.590
Moreover,

24:39.790 --> 24:41.920
His Majesty is devoted to the princess

24:42.070 --> 24:46.130
and has already ordered the Ministry of Rites
to hurry the arrangements.

24:51.830 --> 24:53.160
Lord Fei.

24:54.350 --> 24:55.110
Princess.

24:59.400 --> 25:00.160
Princess.

25:00.400 --> 25:01.440
Why are you awake?

25:01.750 --> 25:02.920
It's already late in the morning—

25:02.920 --> 25:04.270
I can't sleep all day.

25:05.350 --> 25:06.750
Since Lord Fei is here,

25:06.790 --> 25:08.790
let's go see Physician Han.

25:09.070 --> 25:11.330
I haven't seen them since they returned.

25:12.400 --> 25:14.590
I came here today to remind you

25:14.790 --> 25:16.850
to stay away from the east courtyard.

25:17.000 --> 25:19.160
Physician Han and General Xiao

25:19.160 --> 25:21.000
are being quarantined there now.

25:21.000 --> 25:22.110
Why?

25:22.790 --> 25:24.750
The outbreak
in Huangpi Village was severe.

25:24.750 --> 25:25.720
His Majesty

25:25.720 --> 25:27.400
was worried about your health,

25:27.400 --> 25:29.200
so he had no choice but to do this.

25:31.920 --> 25:34.580
I didn't expect
His Majesty to be so thoughtful.

25:35.680 --> 25:36.200
Well,

25:36.270 --> 25:38.470
they must be in need of food and clothes.

25:38.590 --> 25:39.270
Jin Xi.

25:39.310 --> 25:41.240
send them my dried meat

25:41.240 --> 25:42.400
and pastries.

25:46.720 --> 25:47.400
Okay.

25:55.400 --> 25:56.550
This is all the food

25:56.550 --> 25:58.110
we have for now.

25:58.880 --> 26:01.240
Looks like
we'll be stuck here for some time.

26:01.240 --> 26:02.000
Why?

26:02.030 --> 26:03.090
I'm not a prisoner.

26:16.510 --> 26:17.350
Open the door!

26:17.350 --> 26:18.310
Is anyone there?

26:19.920 --> 26:20.830
Is anyone outside?

26:20.830 --> 26:21.790
Open the door!

26:22.070 --> 26:22.880
Open the door!

26:22.880 --> 26:24.830
Let us out!

26:29.920 --> 26:30.440
Jin Xi.

26:31.480 --> 26:32.310
Tell me.

26:32.350 --> 26:34.240
Physician Han and General Xiao

26:34.240 --> 26:35.880
have gone through so much together,

26:35.880 --> 26:37.070
and now they're stuck

26:37.070 --> 26:38.270
in the same yard.

26:38.920 --> 26:41.590
Will they...

26:43.270 --> 26:45.000
Haven't you ever wondered

26:45.200 --> 26:47.310
what it would be like

26:47.480 --> 26:48.940
to be with the one you love?

26:49.640 --> 26:50.270
I...

26:50.400 --> 26:51.440
I haven't.

26:52.720 --> 26:53.960
Really?

26:56.030 --> 26:57.790
You always tease me.

26:58.480 --> 26:59.350
What about you?

26:59.750 --> 27:01.550
Don't you have someone you like?

27:02.720 --> 27:05.200
I think you and Lord Fei

27:05.440 --> 27:06.970
suit each other quite well.

27:08.240 --> 27:09.400
He will

27:09.400 --> 27:11.240
be in charge of your marriage ceremony,

27:11.240 --> 27:12.920
and I serve by your side,

27:12.920 --> 27:13.750
so it's natural that

27:13.750 --> 27:14.950
we have more contact.

27:15.240 --> 27:15.920
Oh.

27:16.110 --> 27:17.270
I see.

27:19.680 --> 27:21.830
You're often with Lord Fei—

27:22.030 --> 27:23.720
has he ever mentioned

27:23.790 --> 27:25.350
General Xiao's siblings?

27:26.720 --> 27:28.000
It seems

27:28.240 --> 27:29.590
he has an elder brother.

27:30.310 --> 27:31.480
What's his name?

27:32.240 --> 27:33.720
I don't know.

27:34.240 --> 27:35.310
But

27:35.310 --> 27:37.590
he came here a few days ago.

27:41.720 --> 27:44.480
So he is General Xiao's brother.

27:46.200 --> 27:48.680
I never thought there could be a man

27:48.680 --> 27:51.080
who is both so childish
and so interesting.

28:00.240 --> 28:03.770
Her Highness's martial skills are truly
no less than any man's.

28:04.000 --> 28:04.920
Her presence

28:05.440 --> 28:07.400
is even more imposing than General Xiao's.

28:07.400 --> 28:08.240
Of course.

28:08.310 --> 28:10.400
Her Highness is truly gifted in
both civil and military arts.

28:10.400 --> 28:11.920
Had she been a man,

28:12.030 --> 28:13.680
she would have ruled with wisdom

28:13.680 --> 28:15.140
and conquered with force.

28:16.550 --> 28:17.750
Don't talk nonsense.

28:17.750 --> 28:18.550
Are you crazy?

28:23.240 --> 28:25.440
His Majesty has arrived!

28:25.440 --> 28:26.200
Xie.

28:28.350 --> 28:29.810
Greetings, Your Majesty.

28:30.070 --> 28:31.240
Get up.

28:31.350 --> 28:32.750
Thank you, Your Majesty.

28:32.960 --> 28:34.960
What brings you here all of a sudden?

28:34.960 --> 28:37.070
Your sword skills have improved.

28:37.200 --> 28:38.660
You came just to praise me?

28:39.200 --> 28:39.720
Yes.

28:39.960 --> 28:41.690
I came specifically to see you.

28:41.880 --> 28:43.000
Just to see me?

28:43.270 --> 28:44.870
Nothing else you want to say?

28:46.480 --> 28:48.210
There is something, actually.

28:48.750 --> 28:49.720
I want

28:50.110 --> 28:53.480
to discuss the timing

28:53.880 --> 28:54.830
of the marriage alliance

28:54.830 --> 28:56.830
with the Changmo princess with you.

28:58.790 --> 29:00.790
She's been in Jinglan for some time.

29:01.000 --> 29:03.460
You've kept her
in the General's residence—

29:03.550 --> 29:05.030
why the sudden thought

29:05.400 --> 29:07.200
of bringing her into the palace?

29:09.790 --> 29:12.480
The alliance is a matter of state.

29:12.750 --> 29:13.960
It shouldn't

29:13.960 --> 29:15.400
be delayed any further.

29:15.480 --> 29:16.480
So,

29:16.680 --> 29:18.110
if we complete the ceremony soon

29:18.110 --> 29:19.480
and restore relations
between the two nations,

29:19.480 --> 29:21.240
the people can live

29:21.240 --> 29:22.270
in lasting peace,

29:22.510 --> 29:23.160
right?

29:27.550 --> 29:28.790
I heard

29:29.310 --> 29:31.510
the Princess of Changmo is a beauty.

29:35.880 --> 29:37.160
I don't know.

29:37.350 --> 29:38.270
Really?

29:38.270 --> 29:39.270
Really.

29:41.960 --> 29:43.680
When is the ceremony set for?

29:44.440 --> 29:46.000
It seems

29:46.350 --> 29:48.030
to be the tenth day of next month.

29:48.030 --> 29:49.160
It's a good day.

29:49.830 --> 29:51.310
You think it's a good day?

29:51.310 --> 29:52.270
Of course.

29:52.640 --> 29:53.680
My closest brother

29:53.680 --> 29:55.410
is marrying the woman he loves—

29:55.480 --> 29:56.960
it's the best day

29:56.960 --> 29:58.440
there could be.
